1 SECTION 3.1. Prosecutions for offenses committed before the effective date of this
2 act are not abated or affected by this act, and the statutes that would be applicable but for this act
3 remain applicable to those prosecutions.
4 SECTION 3.2. Except as otherwise provided in this act, this act is effective when it
5 becomes law.
